    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;Segment Routing can be applied to the IPv6 data plane using a new type of Routing Extension Header called the Segment Routing Header (SRH).  This document describes the SRH and how it is used by nodes that are Segment Routing (SR) capable.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
